WWW-Opentracker-Stats
==================================

Provides an easy to use interface to retrieve various statistics from
opentracker, a BitTorrent tracker.

It executes HTTP requests to opentrackers web services, parses the
response and returns data structures that you can easily extract data from,
to store it in a database or display it on the web.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


See http://erdgeist.org/arts/software/opentracker/ for instructions
of installing opentracker and running.


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

    parent
    Bit::Vector
    Carp
    Class::Accessor::Fast
    Convert::Bencode
    LWP::UserAgent
    Params::Validate

You also need a running opentracker server for this module to be useful.


